# CONTEXT ENGINE — MISTRAL AI HACKATHON VERSION

## Project Overview
We are building Context Engine — an always-on feedback intelligence system for Product Managers. This is a NEW build for the Mistral AI Hackathon (Feb 28 - Mar 1, 2026). We are NOT modifying the Elasticsearch version. We are building a fresh version using Mistral AI + LangChain + LangGraph.

## Reference Project
- REFERENCE FOLDER (READ ONLY, DO NOT MODIFY): D:\LinkedIn\Week4\Hackathon
- This is the working Elasticsearch version of Context Engine. Use it as architectural reference for patterns, data models, frontend components, and business logic.
- Copy and adapt patterns from here. Do not import from it or create dependencies on it.

