- PROJECT FOLDER: D:\LinkedIn\Week4\Mistral AI
- All new code goes here. This is the only folder you write to.

## Tech Stack

### Backend
- Python 3.11+
- FastAPI with uvicorn
- SQLite (replacing Elasticsearch)
- LangChain + LangGraph for agent orchestration
- LangSmith for monitoring and tracing
- Mistral AI as the LLM provider for everything
- MCP for external data source connections
- pip with requirements.txt for dependency management

### Frontend
- React 18 with TypeScript
- Vite as build tool
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- Recharts for dashboard charts
- npm as package manager

### Infrastructure
- Single Docker container
- FastAPI serves the API
- Frontend built as static files

